Me and Ray have got it.

07:03.490 --> 07:04.889
Mom, can I have a beer,
please?

07:04.891 --> 07:07.493
I'll get you a beer
if you entertain.

07:07.495 --> 07:09.762
- TV's cheating!
- TV's entertainment!

