08:04.418 --> 08:05.918
'Maisie's Uncle

08:05.920 --> 08:08.988
'and our very own Blue Hill
County Police Deputy Sheriff,

08:08.990 --> 08:11.990
- 'Kenneth Burroughs.'
- 'Firstly,

08:11.992 --> 08:16.461
'I'd like to thank you all
for coming here today.

08:16.463 --> 08:17.962
'As you are aware,

08:17.964 --> 08:22.637
'it's a year to the day
