08:43.224 --> 08:44.956
'And I'm, uh...

08:44.958 --> 08:49.027
'I'm sure you'll all agree
with me when I say how smart

08:49.029 --> 08:51.899
'and how capable she was.

08:53.801 --> 08:57.203
'Maisie really was very special.

08:57.205 --> 09:01.540
