09:05.245 --> 09:07.014
'All of us.'

09:11.519 --> 09:12.888
No TV.

09:36.043 --> 09:39.545
Do you remember
when Mom died

09:39.547 --> 09:41.914
and Dad would always be off,

09:41.916 --> 09:44.749
working or whatever,

09:44.751 --> 09:46.954
and I had to look after you?

09:51.792 --> 09:54.593
This is the same.

09:54.595 --> 09:57.032
Just a little bit different.

10:03.270 --> 10:05.005
I'm here for you.

10:09.644 --> 10:12.176
Anyway,

10:12.178 --> 10:15.680
it was always me
looking after you, dummy.

10:15.682 --> 10:18.019
No!

10:21.822 --> 10:24.225
Ahem!

10:27.227 --> 10:29.695
You got a drink problem!

10:29.697 --> 10:31.564
