pizza? I don't eat pizza.

10:42.309 --> 10:44.676
I hardly ate any of that.

10:44.678 --> 10:48.613
So, Billy, I was expecting
to see, uh...

10:48.615 --> 10:50.148
- Jeez, what was her name?
- Jenny.

10:50.150 --> 10:53.352
Jenny. That's it.
Is she, uh...

10:53.354 --> 10:56.188
I mean, uh...

10:56.190 --> 10:58.357
What happened to her?
What happened to Jenny?

10:58.359 --> 11:02.062
- It wasn't working out.
- Could you pass the ketchup?

11:04.097 --> 11:06.699
- Noah.
- What?

11:06.701 --> 11:09.068
- Don't.
- Don't what?

11:09.070 --> 11:12.637
Pass the sauce to your uncle
like a normal human being.

11:12.639 --> 11:15.273
Don't pass the sauce to my uncle
like a normal human being?

11:15.275 --> 11:17.943
Just do it, please.

11:17.945 --> 11:21.180
That's a real shame
about Jenny.

11:21.182 --> 11:22.147
She was a great girl.

11:22.149 --> 11:24.682
- Yeah, Jenny's...
- She was a great girl!

11:24.684 --> 11:26.852
Jenny's great. Uhm...

11:26.854 --> 11:28.653
But we had our differences.

11:28.655 --> 11:30.254
- When did it happen?
- Few months back.

11:30.256 --> 11:32.824
I'm sorry to hear that, bud.

11:32.826 --> 11:35.194
It was for the best.

11:35.196 --> 11:38.066
Billy was gonna propose to her.

11:41.369 --> 11:46.041
But he got scared, and
Billy doesn't face his fears.

11:47.774 --> 11:49.407
He just runs.

11:49.409 --> 11:51.278
Ain't that right, Billy?

11:54.148 --> 11:56.084
Yeah, Ray, that's right.

11:58.818 --> 12:00.219
You're a dick!

12:00.221 --> 12:02.090
Not today!

12:03.289 --> 12:05.059
Please, Noah!

12:05.993 --> 12:08.826
Just sit down
and finish your dinner.

12:08.828 --> 12:10.764
I've already finished.

12:16.937 --> 12:20.075
Well, there it is.

12:26.913 --> 12:29.283
Excuse me.

12:33.953 --> 12:37.825
Martha and I
actually planned on having kids.

12:39.693 --> 12:41.193
I just wanted one or two,

12:41.195 --> 12:44.065
but she, like,
wanted twenty or thirty.

12:46.133 --> 12:48.235
You know how she was.

12:49.703 --> 12:52.438
And then, when...

12:52.440 --> 12:55.010
when Martha passed...

12:56.043 --> 12:58.145
I just felt like
my life was over.

12:59.245 --> 13:01.479
I felt crippled,

13:01.481 --> 13:04.248
like life wasn't
worth living anymore.

13:04.250 --> 13:08.389
And then, in time,
I managed to pick myself up.

13:11.826 --> 13:14.229
My life was never over...

13:15.361 --> 13:17.298
It was just hard to see.

13:21.469 --> 13:24.368
Grief is blinding.

13:24.370 --> 13:27.105
- I don't wanna talk about it.
- She needs you right now.

13:27.107 --> 13:30.242
I do not want to talk about it,
Morgan.

13:30.244 --> 13:32.312
I think you need some time.

13:35.081 --> 13:36.147
It's been a year.

13:36.149 --> 13:38.783
But only six hours
since you made peace with it.

13:38.785 --> 13:40.017
Made peace?

13:40.019 --> 13:42.220
You know that ain't
what I'm saying, Ray.

13:42.222 --> 13:46.458
I ain't never
making peace with it.

13:46.460 --> 13:48.363
You know what I mean, Ray!

13:50.297 --> 13:51.430
Oh...

13:51.432 --> 13:53.831
Oh, come on!

13:53.833 --> 13:55.233
Ray!

13:55.235 --> 13:58.173
You know I didn't mean it
to sound like that.

14:03.277 --> 14:04.879
Goddammit.

14:08.115 --> 14:10.250
I searched for days.

14:14.321 --> 14:16.224
I didn't sleep.

14:17.957 --> 14:20.060
I didn't eat.

14:21.461 --> 14:23.298
I didn't stop.

14:24.398 --> 14:26.367
I couldn't...

14:29.302 --> 14:31.002
I know...

14:31.004 --> 14:34.208
I know you know all this,
but...

14:35.842 --> 14:37.843
The truth is...

14:37.845 --> 14:41.216
The truth is...
I let you down.

14:43.017 --> 14:46.020
You, Ray, Noah...
I let this family down.

14:47.520 --> 14:49.423
And that...

14:50.423 --> 14:53.191
that guilt, that...

14:53.193 --> 14:56.264
well, this feeling
of helplessness...

14:58.532 --> 15:01.402
I feel responsibility,
I feel...

15:03.870 --> 15:06.307
I just...
I just wanted you to know...

15:07.607 --> 15:10.441
how sorry I am, Olivia.

15:10.443 --> 15:13.313
This family is everything to me.

15:14.315 --> 15:15.416
Everything.

15:16.317 --> 15:18.986
Stop apologizing.

15:21.455 --> 15:23.191
I'm gonna check on Noah.

16:54.148 --> 16:56.580
- What's up?
- Oh, hey.

16:56.582 --> 16:59.483
- Everything all right?
- Yeah. Yeah, just, uh...

16:59.485 --> 17:02.621
Gregory Mathison's boys
are messing around out back,

17:02.623 --> 17:04.589
lighting flares.

17:04.590 --> 17:07.528
Just gonna go have
a polite word with them.

17:08.428 --> 17:12.229
Ray...
You sure you're all right?

17:12.231 --> 17:14.498
Yeah, I'm fine, Arlene.
Honestly.

17:14.500 --> 17:16.300
I won't be five minutes.

17:16.303 --> 17:18.202
What's the trouble?

17:18.204 --> 17:20.505
Oh, just some kids
messing around out back.

17:20.507 --> 17:22.673
He wants to go have
a polite word with them.

17:22.675 --> 17:25.609
They're playing with those
goddamn flares again.

17:25.612 --> 17:28.580
They'll spook the dog.
It could be dangerous.

17:28.582 --> 17:31.182
Well, Reese Jordan's on duty.
I'll give him a call.

17:31.184 --> 17:32.450
- Yeah.
- God!

17:32.452 --> 17:34.419
Maybe it's best.
Just leave it to the Sheriff.

17:34.421 --> 17:36.090
Olivia!

17:38.692 --> 17:40.191
Look...

17:40.193 --> 17:42.526
I'm just gonna drive down
the track, cut them off,

17:42.528 --> 17:44.662
have a civilized conversation
with them.

17:44.664 --> 17:47.132
Failing that, I'll drive
straight to their home

17:47.134 --> 17:48.632
and have a civilized
conversation

17:48.634 --> 17:50.434
with Gregory Mathison instead.

17:50.436 --> 17:52.770
The last time you had a
civilized conversation with him

17:52.772 --> 17:55.606
you ended up spending the night
in a cell, remember?

17:55.608 --> 17:58.075
Gee, thanks for that
convenient reminder, Billy.

17:58.077 --> 17:59.544
Anytime, Ray.

17:59.546 --> 18:02.146
- Well, you're not going alone.
- Oh, God!

18:02.148 --> 18:04.382
- I'm coming, too.
- No, no, you're staying.

18:04.384 --> 18:05.549
- Dad, come on.
- No.

18:05.551 --> 18:07.151
- Take him with you.
- Olivia.

18:07.153 --> 18:09.554
Just take him, Ray.

18:09.556 --> 18:11.590
Oh, Jesus Christ!

18:11.592 --> 18:14.026
Let me guess -
you're coming, too?

18:14.028 --> 18:16.594
