otherwise.

18:16.596 --> 18:17.664
Me too.

18:19.400 --> 18:21.703
A goddamn circus this is.

18:35.082 --> 18:37.352
You should talk to him.

18:39.619 --> 18:42.487
It doesn't matter what's going
on between you and Olivia, Ray.

18:42.489 --> 18:44.592
You need to talk to your son.

18:51.531 --> 18:54.199
Yeah, shit like that, Ray.

18:54.201 --> 18:57.602
- He'll end up hating you.
- My God, stop!

18:57.604 --> 19:00.671
Is he your son?

19:00.673 --> 19:02.576
No, he's mine.

19:03.644 --> 19:06.413
Sit back and shut up.

19:08.548 --> 19:10.651
I hate saying, "Told you so."

19:27.401 --> 19:29.668
Take advice from
my younger brother...

19:29.670 --> 19:30.735
All right...

19:30.737 --> 19:32.370
What life experience
do you have?

19:32.372 --> 19:35.306
- Let it go, guys, let it go.
- Huh?

19:35.308 --> 19:37.441
What life experience
do you have?

19:37.443 --> 19:39.210
I know what it's like
to not like your dad.

19:39.212 --> 19:41.746
You know what it's like
to raise a family?

19:41.748 --> 19:43.418
