under your seat.

20:07.641 --> 20:10.909
I fail to see
how that's gonna help, Ray.

20:10.911 --> 20:12.611
Stay here with Noah.

20:12.613 --> 20:13.578
Ray!

20:13.580 --> 20:16.914
No problem, Ray.
I can do that for you, Ray.

20:16.916 --> 20:20.619
Thanks for asking
ever so kindly, Ray.

20:20.621 --> 20:23.591
Ray! Ray!
Will you slow down?

20:24.857 --> 20:26.391
What's with the weapon?

20:26.393 --> 20:28.860
- Ain't gonna use it, Ken.
- Besides the point.

20:28.862 --> 20:31.595
Look, if we run into these kids
out here messing around,

20:31.597 --> 20:35.600
you just let me do the talking,
right?

20:35.602 --> 20:38.702
So what do we do if the Mathison
boys run out in front of us?

20:38.704 --> 20:40.639
We chase after them.

20:40.641 --> 20:43.607
- What if they don't run?
- Catch 'em.

20:43.609 --> 20:46.911
- And then what?
- We beat 'em up.

20:46.913 --> 20:48.779
Ain't that a little barbaric?

20:48.781 --> 20:51.682
